{
  "stem": "14552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and then I was born.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every one of them, till just recently, they all thought of me always as the baby, and always spoiled me and loved me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I had a very-- I had a very nice family setup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very loyal and loving to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were known as the most loyal family around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were in a Czechish-- we were Czechs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had the-- go to school and do our lifestyle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was this-- we had a very good life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What we didn't like under the Czechs was the taxing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted an awful lot of tax.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they got it best they could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would [LAUGHS] search for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't even know how well we had it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father was a Hungarian in his soul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All he wanted is the peacetime, [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wanted to have it from the time that he remembered in Hungary, that it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we all lived for the time when we'll be reoccupied by Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was living in a-- in the wrong world because the Czechs were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had their-- they had their little schtickle, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had-- they were not-- they were not anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there were people there who, who just didn't befriend the Jews all that much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we were onto ourselves mostly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And life under the Czechs was good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had the money in Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Every child had a sum put away in Prague, which we never retrieved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We never got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know why that we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't go after it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So it was lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
